title: The Mecca of the  “one stop shopping” experience for the average income human.
text: I had seen ads for SHEIN on Instagram but never really paid any mind. You know more things to get sucked into that cause more money to be spent. But then when I was at the hair salon with my stylist I complimented her on the cutest earrings and clothes and she said she got a them off SHEIN! And then told me about the bed set she bought for her daughter and so on. Wow! My eyes were opened to how this app works and how many options of any product you have to choose from! AND affordability is the main reason I shop on here like 2x a month LoL I have bought items all the way from mattify ing  skin care powders and the brushes to cute tops and hats! And the quality is great every time!! I honestly wish I would have clicked on those ads on social media earlier. LoL I would have been window shopping  and then buying and NOT breaking my bank way before just this last month LoL. Never go away SHEIN! And I owe my new shopping addiction to my hair stylist, Shellie.
